705188f-a.text:
Kent Avenue, north irom South 9th Street toward the Williamsburg Bridge. At the northeast corner of South 8th Street is the Harris paint factory. This building, and others extending to Broadway, can be seen in view 2.
P. L. Sperr  April 11, 1931
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
